title: 198: Cutler's Dolphins debut, Bortles done?
itunes:title: 198: Cutler's Dolphins debut, Bortles done?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks review and preview all the action from preseason week 2. DJ also takes you behind the scenes of FSU's program after a week in Tallahassee. The guys also reveal under the radar 2018 prospects before sitting down with a running back on the list, Arizona State's Kalen Ballage.
